  // Overview
  section.overview(style="padding-left: 300px; padding-right: 300px;")
    h2 About Secure My Campus
    p Secure My Campus is a comprehensive platform designed to enhance safety, transparency, and communication on college campuses. It enables students and staff to report issuesâ€”including maintenance, safety concerns, and harassmentâ€”and monitor their resolution in real time. The platform also features a smart Lost & Found system and secure administrative tools for efficient management. By streamlining communication and accountability, it fosters a responsive and well-organized campus environment. Accessible, reliable, and user-friendly, Secure My Campus ensures a safer and more connected campus experience.

  // Stats Section
